<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "chase.jpg", width: "300", height: "400", alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div 
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              ></div>
            </div>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-8">
       <p>Hello, Welcome to the about-me section of my personal portfolio. My name is Chase Story, I am 23 years young, and only recently discovered that being a Developer is something that not only interests me, but provides me the opportunity to utilize both my creative, and logical sides. </p>

        <p> Although, it took me a bit longer to discover this amazing career field, I could never work in a different enviornment again. Technology is the future, and I am enlightened to not only be a part of it, but also be a contributing member to our future. Please feel free to browse my portfolio, and contact me with any questions you may have! Namaste.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
